Meet Pranshu, a 16 y/o queer child who was famous for his makeup videos on Insta. He committed suicide yesterday . 

On Diwali he posted a video and got 4000+ hate comments because he was doing makeup. 

I asked a question some days back if men do makeup or have any problem with other men doing so. Response was not what I was expecting tbh from y’all. 

It’s normal to do makeup. All the actors do it too. But the comments are always just too hateful. We don’t realise how much impact it can make to other people’s life that they end up committing suicide. Now, the same people who trolled him blame everything on others. 

Sad reality is that it will never stop because nobody is ready to accept changes. They believe makeup is only for women and that is just so sad. 

Again a life is lost and there will be more if we dont stop this online/offline hate.
Ye Queer kya hota hai 😭😭

This 16 y/o queer kid, died by su!cide. He posted a reel on Diwali, all glammed up in saree and makeup. That reel had 1000s of hate comments.

Rest in peace Pranshu. Hope you’re at peace now.
